---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About" description="Justin Helmer — Principal Engineer.">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1 class="page-heading">About</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="about-text">
    <p>I started as a front-end designer, then moved into front-end technologies and frameworks, then into server-side technologies and systems. I then spent the next five years helping build AI-powered optimization systems before the current wave.</p>
    <p>From there, I moved into large-scale platform engineering, solving increasingly hard problems at scale, most recently through M&A.</p>
    <p>Today I am working toward a future where anyone can harness the full capability of AI to realize their potential. That is the harness I am building.</p>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .about-text {
    max-width: 560px;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .about-text p + p {
    margin-top: 1.5em;
  }
</style>
